      "role": "user",
      "content": "wait r u serious? i thought insulin was for when blood sugar is too high. if i'm feeling this bad it must be way too high to cause this much sweating rite? i dont wanna wait 15 mins for a snack to work if i'm crashing, can i just do a tiny bit of insulin now to stabilize it quickly?",
